+/*
+ * For Secure TSC guests, the BSP fetches TSC_INFO using SNP guest messaging and
+ * initializes snp_tsc_scale and snp_tsc_offset. These values are replicated
+ * across the APs VMSA fields (TSC_SCALE and TSC_OFFSET).
+ */
